Other popular resources such as ConceptNet [speer2017conceptnet], GenericsKB [bhakthavatsalam2020genericskb], Ascent/Ascent++ [ascent,ascentpp], ATOMIC [atomic], ASER [zhang2020aser] and TransOMCS [transomcs] do not have their focus on cultural knowledge and contain very little to zero assertions for geography or religion subjects, hence, they are not qualified for this comparison.